@Sjors actually it's not necessary as `CWalletTx` caches the value.

> #12508 replaces the IsFromMe function making this redundant if that is merged, correct?

@MeshCollider that was closed.

Anyway, this only improves performance for transaction with wallet inputs upfront, which avoids computing remaining input debits.

@laanwj @MarcoFalke this change is really simple but not worth the effort to benchmark. Feel free to close if it's not mergeable.
